 * | Ctrl | Alt  | Meta | Alt  |             | Meta | Space| Lower | | Raise | Enter | RAlt |             | LEFT | DOWN | UP   | RIGHT|
 * .----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------.
 */

            bindings = <
&kp GRAVE   &kp N1    &kp N2     &kp N3              &kp N4  &kp N5                                                               &kp N6  &kp N7  &kp N8     &kp N9    &kp N0     &kp BACKSPACE
&kp TAB     &kp Q     &kp W      &kp E               &kp R   &kp T                                                                &kp Y   &kp U   &kp I      &kp O     &kp P      &kp BSLH
&kp ESCAPE  &kp A     &kp S      &kp D               &kp F   &kp G                                                                &kp H   &kp J   &kp K      &kp L     &kp SEMI   &kp SQT
&kp LSHFT   &kp Z     &kp X      &kp C               &kp V   &kp B              &mo 3  &kp PG_UP      &kp HOME  &mo 4             &kp N   &kp M   &kp COMMA  &kp DOT   &kp SLASH  &kp RIGHT_SHIFT
&kp LCTRL   &kp LALT  &kp LMETA  &kp LC(LEFT_SHIFT)                  &kp SPACE  &mo 1  &kp PAGE_DOWN  &kp END   &mo 2  &kp ENTER                  &kp LEFT   &kp DOWN  &kp UP     &kp RIGHT
            >;
